Sentencas: Bilayers comprised of dense and porous YSZ-Al2O3 (20 wt%) composite were tape cast, processed, and then fabricated into working solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs).
Titulo: Heterogeneous electrolyte (YSZ-Al2O3) based direct oxidation solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The porous part of the bilayer was converted into anode for direct oxidation of fuels by infiltrating CeO2 and Cu.
Titulo: Heterogeneous electrolyte (YSZ-Al2O3) based direct oxidation solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: Several button cells were evaluated under hydrogen/air and propane/air atmospheres in intermediate temperature range and their performance data were analyzed.
Titulo: Heterogeneous electrolyte (YSZ-Al2O3) based direct oxidation solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: For the first time the feasibility of using YSZ-Al2O3 material for fabricating working SOFCs with high open circuit voltage (OCV) and power density is demonstrated.
Titulo: Heterogeneous electrolyte (YSZ-Al2O3) based direct oxidation solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: AC impedance spectroscopy and scanning electron microscopy (SEM) techniques were used to characterize the membrane and cell.
